## 🛠️ Comandos de desarrollo

```bash
make run        # levanta servidor con hot-reload
make lint       # ruff check
make format     # ruff format
make typecheck  # mypy
make test       # pytest
make check      # lint + typecheck + test
```

---

## ➕ Agregar un nuevo router

1. Crea `app/routers/mi_recurso.py` siguiendo el patrón de `items.py`
2. Crea `app/schemas/mi_recurso.py` con los modelos Pydantic
3. Regístralo en `app/main.py`:

```python
from app.routers import mi_recurso
app.include_router(mi_recurso.router, prefix="/api/v1")
```

---

## 🔐 Autenticación con Supabase Auth (opcional)

```python
from fastapi import Security, HTTPException
from fastapi.security import HTTPBearer, HTTPAuthorizationCredentials

security = HTTPBearer()

def get_current_user(credentials: HTTPAuthorizationCredentials = Security(security)):
    token = credentials.credentials
    db = get_supabase()
    user = db.auth.get_user(token)
    if not user:
        raise HTTPException(status_code=401, detail="Token inválido")
    return user
```
